      "value": "What is Flexbox?"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "value": "Flexbox is a one-dimensional layout system used to arrange elements in rows or columns with flexible sizing and alignment."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Flex Container"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
